                     <interp inst="t17771203-17-off104" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing nine engine screws made of mixed metal, value 6 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17771203-17-victim211" type="victimName">
                     Samuel
                      Hadley
                  <interp inst="t17771203-17-victim211" type="surname" value="Hadley"></interp>
